cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.DC, cs.SI 

This paper deals with the analysis of smart contracts on the Ethereum blockchain to identify token systems. It involves techniques such as symbolic execution and exploits the common interface of ERC-20. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
